    <bioghist>
      <head>Biography/History</head>
      <p>Mr. and Mrs. James L. Britton III were natives of Nashville, Tennessee, with Mrs. Britton being a 1958 graduate of Vanderbilt University.</p>
    </bioghist>
    <scopecontent>
      <head>Scope and Contents</head>
      <p>This collection contains 13 rare Nineteenth Century imprints relating to the State of Tennessee. The .21 linear feet of material will be housed in 13 file folders and stored in a manuscript box.</p>
    </scopecontent>
